Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:13.98,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本  种垣岛宇宙中心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.25,0:00:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡罗琳大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.69,0:00:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五天后我们就在宇宙了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.55,0:00:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.80,0:00:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来\N就只剩离开地面尽力完成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.43,0:00:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  还不能走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他在这个国家吧  光一…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…有谁在…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.32,0:00:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身体里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慎重地执行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.66,0:02:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.71,0:02:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Children  解禁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么看都超可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太空歌剧的主角也是OK的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.90,0:02:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会拯救你于千钧一发之际
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电光火石华尔兹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对·可怜·Children
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.68,0:02:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是假想宇宙空间的任务而进行的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.45,0:02:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先  薰你用念力\N让卫星从穿梭机的货舱里脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像对待女孩子一样温柔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.46,0:02:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你这比喻很像大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.12,0:02:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念动…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅我吧  大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道不愿意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点都不温柔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就是性骚扰嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.85,0:02:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是这么玩的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}请原谅我吧  大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明显是自己在打转
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.79,0:03:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这种事情根本无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.07,0:03:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能责备薰  皆本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们平时\N都没怎么被当成女孩子来对待嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.68,0:03:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以搞不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是直属上司
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是觉得自己日益成长\N越来越有女人味了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.75,0:03:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  两厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也一步步地\N走向大人的玻璃台阶了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  只是在H{\fs32}2{\r}O里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.05,0:03:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(680,570)\fad(500,500)}43rd  sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.05,0:03:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(780,600)\fad(500,500)}「天作之合！卡罗琳、命运的重逢」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  头发伤到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么非要进行这种训练啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.98,0:03:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没听说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日米共同计划的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本和柯美利亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为国际月球空间站的建设终于要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国际月球空间站？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.99,0:03:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要发射\N为此准备的宇宙穿梭机了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对这种事情没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是关于五天后  就要发射宇宙穿梭机的日米共同计划的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国际月球空间站建设的新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是说曹操…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她  卡罗琳·玛吉小姐是LV2的念动能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡罗琳…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是为了调查  长期宇宙生活会对超能力产生怎样的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,80B
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且算是个美人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.21,0:04:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…和这种…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有些不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要含糊其辞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这花心大萝卜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龌龊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.97,0:04:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和…和小孩子没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Double Face
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入口处严重损坏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有什么人入侵了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入侵者是超能力者的可能性很大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请做好警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入侵者是超能力者？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.94,0:05:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光一
