Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是强力的思念波
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才电视上不是说她是LV2的超能力者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LV6…不  LV7
