Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆本  闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆本  这女人是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转向我这边啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆本
